    License:  Apache-2.0

  YOLO detection  (yolo11l_bbox_v8-trt.onnx)
  YOLO segmentation  (conv_seg_v6-trt.onnx)
    Upstream: Ultralytics YOLO (https://github.com/ultralytics/ultralytics)
    License:  AGPL-3.0
    NOTE: AGPL-3.0 imposes obligations (including source-availability for network
